{"tid":2326269,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"195萬名中共黨員名單懷疑外洩，據指有任職跨國企業及使領館","createTime":"2020-12-15T08:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T09:19:00.000Z","uid":278587,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bbe4ee437553117e0e87fb8a272a1a056635b24f","tid":2326269,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T08:12:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=416659\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416659&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGLyGpUrO7QrNXIpVIwIXQug%3D&h=2268440d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416659&h=5bcde60f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=416659</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】多間傳媒發表調查報道，引述一份聲稱外洩的195萬名中國共產黨員名單，當中不少人任職跨國企業、大學以至外國使領館，被質疑是中共滲透手段。<br />\n<br />\n外洩的中國共產黨員名單，最先在通訊軟件Telegram流傳，來自上海一個伺服器，由一名異見人士取得，交予跨國議員組織對華政策跨國議會聯盟，核實後再由英國、澳洲、比利時和瑞典四間傳媒發表調查報道。<br />\n<br />\n名單涉及195萬名中共黨員資料，包括姓名、職位、地址、電話，顯示他們已滲透眾多跨國企業、大學及外交機關等，包括英國、美國、澳洲等十國駐上海的領事館。當中涉及的英國領事館員工，工作地點跟軍情六處小組近在咫尺，經中國國營人力資源公司的黨支部僱用。<br />\n<br />\n據稱有至少二百幾名中共黨員，為過百家上海的外國機構工作。滙豐及渣打銀行2016年共聘用六百多中共黨員。多間國防企業如波音、空中巴士、勞斯萊斯及大藥廠如輝瑞、阿斯利康葛蘭素史克等，均僱用數以百計的中共黨員。<br />\n<br />\n報道強調，沒有證據顯示這些中共黨員從事間諜活動，但已足以引起多國朝野關注。<br />\n<br />\n英國國會三十名議員聯署要求展開緊急辯論，保守黨前黨魁施志安指，英國企業和大學過於天真，沒認識到中共正摧毀「我們的生活方式」。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲安全情報組織亦展開調查，有國會議員指，當局絕對需要確保事件，沒有涉及外國勢力干預和檢討使領館聘用當地人員的安全問題。"},{"pid":"84f4875a164279246886a5a9b1be6520ba2420fd","tid":2326269,"uid":254383,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T08:39:50.000Z","msg":"幾時有名單"},{"pid":"1dcedc5f1ca10c3ebaa0cd178bec6be5f0b46955","tid":2326269,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T08:41:01.000Z","msg":"大抓捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cdf458c7f3b61edd39601fd1bce474f5c605062","tid":2326269,"uid":39914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T08:41:11.000Z","msg":"厲害了 我的國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e3b363e5b3d56c829a9c3523d4dab32f9b353e","tid":2326269,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T08:41:46.000Z","msg":"快d流出俾神獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"848fa78b4472afb717a3dc87ff6495f18224aec5","tid":2326269,"uid":262557,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T08:47:43.000Z","msg":"左膠又睇唔到"},{"pid":"bf2a6b106b12ad44f204c88f9aeb73430a0c8a55","tid":2326269,"uid":118031,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T08:52:19.000Z","msg":"間諜名單<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf8c7e6fe2dbfd39f408bd36fbff7dbdf235078","tid":2326269,"uid":163801,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T08:53:58.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪換取唔被制裁嘅手段....<br />\n真係邊個冇俾制裁邊個就係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18bf75681296b85b13ea4e2e69708aab196b114a","tid":2326269,"uid":290314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T09:19:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}